keep.name: Warschauer Straße 47
keep.description: Ole from Photoautomat sent word of their first color booth, placed outside at Warschauer Straße 47. The booth is about one minute from the East Side Gallery, the "famous leftovers of the Berlin Wall, next to Oberbaumbrücke." **UPDATE** 8/10/19: This color booth is still turning out beautiful photos as of August, 2019, now with black (rather than white) borders. **UPDATE** 5/4/22: Stephanie reports that this booth is no longer located here. Contributed by Ole Kretschmann, Brian, Stephanie.
